      "firm_id": "optimistic_5",
      "description": "Looking for a rewarding project or a reliable source for parts? This vehicle has seen plenty of life and is ready for someone with a vision to take it on! While it currently requires significant mechanical and cosmetic attention, it offers a fantastic opportunity for a dedicated enthusiast to restore it to its former glory or utilize its components. Priced to move and ready for its next chapter!",
